name: Berry_HD
description:
A mixed model between Berry Mix and Hentai Diffusion 1.8, adding more NSFW image generation capability including suggestive content. Based from Stable Diffusion 1.5. Able to generate images of anime characters, either in 2D or realistic, depending on what kind of prompts that you are putting into. Compatible with vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned.ckpt model (use it for better results).

Newer versions now re-merging original Berry's Mix with Hentai Diffusion 22 while its VAE now baked inside the model. Sample images for newest version now generated under InvokeAI.

For more vivid lighting, recommended to use Light & Shadow LORA model.

Warning: This model is focused solely on NSFW image generation. You must be at least 18 years old or above before using this model. I an not responsible if anything happens during the usage of this model below the legal age.
